   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Agathon to Patron, greeting. On receipt of my letter send a guard to the Arsinoite nome to get for us the best donkeys possible; do this quickly and send them to us at the city. Goodbye. (Addressed on the verso): To Patron.</ab>
         </div>
